                    <h2>PATRIC</h2>
                    <p>The Pathosystems Resource Integration Center, PATRIC, is the legacy Bacterial Bioinformatics Resource Center (BRC), representing 15 years of progressive development and service to bacterial researchers. PATRIC sharpens and hones the scope of available bacterial phylogenomic data from numerous sources in order to save biologists time and effort when conducting comparative analyses. The freely available PATRIC platform provides an interface for biologists to discover data and information and conduct comprehensive comparative genomics and other analyses in a one-stop shop.</p>
